Welcome to Mephisto Soul, a Linux Chess and Instant Messaging Program!

To install Mephisto Soul from Chat_Beta release,
	1) Program is already installed. 
	2) Check out README for more info on how to run Mephisto Soul. 
		Have fun!

To install Mephisto Soul from Chat_Beta_src release,
	1) Run the command 'make'
	2) Check out README for more info on how to run Mephisto Soul
		Then, enjoy!

